When using QuHealthy and its teleconsultation and video call tools, it is strictly prohibited to: 
(1) Upload in bad faith, illicit, defamatory material, viruses or software interruptions; 
(2) Infringe the bases of the electronic clinical record regulations (NOM-024-SSA3-2012);
(3) Record, broadcast or perform acts without prior express and formal consent; 
(4) Impersonate clinical identity. 
Any transgressor will be reported to the corresponding penal jurisdiction, in addition to the immediate cancellation of their portal privileges.
